data.description: Welcome to 1617 Alston Road in Towson, Maryland! Nestled in the desirable Valley Country Club neighborhood, this stunning home offers the perfect combination of convenience and beauty. Boasting four bedrooms and three full baths, this open floor plan home is truly a gem. As you enter, you'll be greeted by a modern and spacious kitchen featuring stainless steel appliances, sleek blue cabinets, and an aesthetically pleasing backsplash. The great room is truly a focal point of the house, featuring a wood-burning fireplace and vaulted ceilings, creating a cozy and inviting atmosphere. The three-season room is a fantastic addition, providing the perfect space for entertaining guests or simply enjoying some peace and tranquility. Step outside onto the patio and you'll appreciate the privacy of the flat yard, offering endless possibilities for outdoor activities and relaxation. The fully finished basement is a great bonus, complete with custom tile bathroom and plenty of natural light. With the favorable blue ribbon school districts, this home offers the perfect place to raise a family and provide them with an exceptional education. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this beautiful property your own. With its modern features, convenient location, and abundance of natural light, this home truly has it all. Schedule a showing today and discover all the wonderful amenities and features that 1617 Alston Road has to offer.
